txt.en: 'The Armoury is rebuilt, but now it must be prepared to hold our armour. We also must get it ready for the workers who will sharpen and repair our weapons. There is much to do in order to get the Armoury fully stocked and ready to defend us when the next assault comes.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
